text: Alex Wright (born May 17, 1975) is a German former professional wrestler. He is probably best known for wrestling for the now defunct WCW where he was a one time WCW Cruiserweight Champion, one time WCW World Tag Team Champion with Disco Inferno, and one time WCW World Television Champion. == References == Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Nuremberg Category:Professional wrestlers
title: Alex Wright
